      "publishedDate": "2024-05-15",
      "readDate": "2026-03-28",
      "language": "en",
      "abstract": "A comprehensive guide to scaling monolithic systems, covering performance optimization, database indexing, frontend performance issues, team dynamics, monitoring, and best practices.",
